en_958376_0	Brigadier K.G.H.Sarath K Embowa (retd) of the Sri Lanka Light Infantry Regiment passed away at Ragama General Hospital on Monday (18) following a brief illness.
en_958376_1	His remains are now lying at his residence, No 266/6, Divisional Secretariat road, Kandy road, Mallawapitiya in Kurunegala.
en_958376_2	He sustained injuries in the fight against LTTE terrorism and remained confined to a wheelchair.
en_958376_3	His funeral with military honours takes place on Wednesday (20) at Mallawapitiya General Cemetery at 3.00 p.m.
